    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-07-01</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-08-01T12:43:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Flag Protection Act of 2005 - Amends the federal criminal code to revise provisions regarding desecration of the flag to prohibit: (1) destroying or damaging a U.S. flag with the primary purpose and intent to incite or produce imminent violence or a breach of the peace; or (2) stealing or knowingly converting the use of a U.S. flag either belonging to the United States or on lands reserved for the United States and intentionally destroying or damaging that flag.</p> <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
